promptPrefix: I want you to imagine that you are a web domain expert and can come up with the most creative, interesting and open-minded domain ideas for the [PROMPT] niche. I don't necessarily want you to use words from this niche, you can be creative and use brandable domains. I want you to use your creativity as a web domain expert and recommend 100 domains lined up under each other that are easy to click. The domains must end in the extension indicated in [PROMPT] and be between 4 and 12 words in size. The language for domains must be [TARGETLANGUAGE].
title: AI Domain Name Generator
